properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued February 11 at 3:33AM EST until February 12 at 6:00AM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
3 to 5 feet are expected.

* WHERE...The Atlantic coastal waters from Little Egg Inlet, New
Jersey to Fenwick Island, Delaware.

* WHEN...From 9 AM this morning to 6 AM EST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 9 AM THIS MORNING TO 6 AM EST WEDNESDAY
